{"type": "article", "id": 59246, "title": "可随身携带的盲文打印机，用起来也很简便｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-12-12T22:57:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 55037, "name": "Gumpo"}, {"id": 55038, "name": "Miio Studio"}, {"id": 44025, "name": "WUU"}, {"id": 55039, "name": "Vrailler"}, {"id": 55040, "name": "Gerhardt Kellermann"}, {"id": 55041, "name": "Tim Panek"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 139, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181212200018Gcd1az8CJHNXDYbm.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #fc1454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #fc1454} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Vrailler </h3><p>对于视觉障碍的人来说，完全的包容性总是很难实现。鉴于眼睛是所有感官中最重要的，它的缺失常常会抑制我们读取消费信息、数据和内容的方式，而针对视觉障碍的设计常常是一个巨大的挑战，盲文仍然不是在所有地方都完全可用。这主要是因为盲文打印机是非常专业的机器，而且价格不菲。</p><p>Vrailler 是一款易于使用的盲文打印机，体积小，可以放进口袋，更重要的是，价格实惠。它使用穿孔石板和一组销钉，用户可以将其放入基础石板中创建凹痕。</p><p>当你把上面的石板和中间的石板压在基础石板上，压痕就会在纸上转换，从而得到印刷盲文。这些可以用来创建姓名、标签，甚至是名片。你可以在 Vrailler 上打印多个图钉，一旦你设置了引脚的形状，Vrailler 就可以为你打印盲文，而无需使用任何电力或电池。售价 35 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/vrailler/vrailler-the-portable-and-easy-to-use-braille-prin?ref=8nk47n\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812122001053o1YbDfUO76MsNHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200105RSMEsF0eWnLqUQDo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200105NBQOak7fcqAGX23R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200106lq8NUaZerBwx1nHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200106WGCRoNBSceyzKwJX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200107LOqynmg7p1dztHV4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200107LEQMlHZ7FmJXuGTO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bripe Coffee Brew Pipe Kit by Tim Panek</h3><p>设计师 Tim Panek 设计了这款有趣的创意烟斗咖啡机，其铜管中带有一个小吸管，用软木把手进行绝缘。可以从咖啡机上吸咖啡。此款咖啡机虽然小巧，但是五脏俱全，不但拥有食物温度计，还拥有喷火器，以及可以放置咖啡渣的小瓶子。售价 59.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B06XPSFYJB/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?tag=yankodesign05-20&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;linkId=f8e3b4be305d6a9ee7925c454aad18fb\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200153LZ0h2wkQaT1vsPVM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200153XpleUghjxOcI7R2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200153mfuJvxpEi0yhg7Q3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200158zNI6b7QorcwFVsnA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200158fxgyzneCqGPEmi9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200158JGL7eDkbA86j2VU9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.767619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200158iPHysVaDQ3b0rcO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200158oOktUSLPF3Bgfc6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rings Tray by WUU</h3><p>独立家居设计品牌 WUU 推出新品圆环托盘，它以剧院、广场般的宽阔感为物品提供充裕的放置空间，无论是晨间早点或下午茶歇。</p><p>整个托盘以片状结构作为主体与支撑，自然流畅的倾斜角度、精细的连接点，每一处细节都经过严格的加工处理。圆环与盘底间隔的距离，恰好为托盘的端取提供了舒适的空间。</p><p>设计师为 Rings Tray 调配了三种浪漫的色彩——豆绿灰、岩石白与落日橘，它们以细致粉末喷涂的方式附着于金属表面，触感与观感同样细腻。售价 699 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.3-c-s.w4002-16344133536.93.301a3bd8k1N3qr&amp;id=583953082845\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200235rkQP3RGpBi6bNwHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200235vcVAGUqrluL1OeKQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200235uCDkUts0ZSHaJBAV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200235BetLfyOI4k6rqZuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200236r1M0bZv7LCE4IJxu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>THE BIRD by Baptiste Maingon of Miio Studio</h3><p>什么样的闹钟铃声不会让你的起床气爆发？如果是一只鸟发出的温柔的旋律，会不会让你醒来时舒心一点。</p><p>THE BIRD 是一款设计精美的闹钟，无论用户身在何处，都能选择独特的旋律唤醒你。这不仅可以以更温和的方式开启新的一天，而且还可以阻止你醒来第一件事就是查阅手机屏幕。</p><p>看似无按钮的设计可能会让你疑惑它的操作问题，但这些设置和控制功能都被藏进了用户的智能手机上，且智能手机还可以放在无线充电基座上。只需将木鸟从其栖息处抬起来，闹钟就会被关闭，这是一种与设备交互的好方法。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812122003053cXuRfob8OzH2FP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200305A9wXOHUR6hVvesPK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200305fNjJs6aE2tUkzGLP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.469524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200306quYWaREDJoknczQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200306ZIsDhPEvFpWjLweY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200306OFnwVUzHD3axsRfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200306LMFOQzS7hCBP2s4p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/12/10/a-more-pleasant-way-to-start-your-day/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Desig</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>DITO by Gerhardt Kellermann for <span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Gumpo</span></h3><p>会议桌可以说是很多办公室、会议室或是工作室的必需品，DITO 或许是个不错的选择。</p><p>它是一个摩登现代的会议桌，聚焦于办公人士和会议办公场景的精细化需求。每个公司可能对会议室的用途需求不同，这款可配置、可调节的桌面可以满足不同需求。</p><p>中心分割区域不仅强化了其简洁利落的设计风格，而且还允许电缆穿过位于其下方的网格，连接到更多的通信设备。</p><p>与 DITO 的白色桌面区域形成鲜明对比的，是中央托盘和插座区域，两者都强化了这款会议桌的多功能性，丰富了它的使用场景的可能性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200349Mgciq2XBnWGut7Fp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200349YSasgHzneVclRFAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200350lSbH3f1LPjxv7kqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200350PjOYS6h3Tldvf0iy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200350CPSmAxHdbWluOV2t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200350KH3v9dg0jFA2VBYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181212200418H6psUfi4OFPYIMtj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.gumpo.de/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gumpo</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}